msgctxt "56_Officer"
msgid "Dammit! Where did he go!?"
msgstr "¡Mierda! ¡¿A dónde se fue?!"

msgctxt "68_Tanimura"
msgid "Yo. Where's this wanted criminal you were talking about on the radio?"
msgstr "Oye. ¿Dónde está el criminal del que hablaban por la radio?"

msgctxt "80_Officer"
msgid "Hey, Tanimura-san. Well, you see, we kind of lost him..."
msgstr "Hola, Tanimura-san. Bueno, verás, lo hemos perdido..."

msgctxt "92_Tanimura"
msgid "That's too bad... Well, guess I'll look around for him."
msgstr "Qué lástima... Bueno, miraré alrededor por si lo veo."

msgctxt "176_Shady Man"
msgid "*pant* *pant* These cops don't give up..."
msgstr "*jadeo* *jadeo* Estos policías no se rinden..."

msgctxt "188_Tanimura"
msgid "(Hm? Is that the wanted criminal that's on the run?)"
msgstr "(¿Mm? ¿No será ese el criminal que escapo?)"

msgctxt "200_Tanimura"
msgid "Hey, you there. Can I talk to you?"
msgstr "Oye, tú. ¿Puedo hablar contigo un segundo?"

msgctxt "212_Shady Man"
msgid "Damn! A cop! You'll never take me in!"
msgstr "¡Maldición! ¡Un policía! ¡Nunca me atraparás!"

msgctxt "224_Tanimura"
msgid "If you come along with me, we can avoid any unnecessary violence."
msgstr "Si vienes conmigo, evitaremos cualquier violencia innecesaria."

msgctxt "236_Shady Man"
msgid "I can't afford to get caught! Sorry, pal, but you're going to have to die!"
msgstr "¡No voy a permitirlo! ¡Lo siento amigo, pero vas a tener que\n"
"morir!"

